                <note rend="inline" type="source">713.1311/109: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Costa Rica (<persName type="to">Eberhardt</persName>)</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-11-16T18:00:00-05:00"
                            >November 16, 1932—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>38. Your 70, November 15, 2 p.m. Please continue to keep Department fully
                    informed and in case Foreign Minister <persName corresp="#p_PL1"
                        >Pacheco</persName> proceeds to Guatemala keep the Legation there, as well
                    as the other Legations in Central America, appropriately informed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_SHL1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
